				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Cycle-timed Y position detection (white screen, timing from sprite 0 to the hit) allows the search to be narrowed down to plus or minus about 15 scanlines. Then a binary (as opposed to linear) search reduces the number of frames needed to narrow down which object was hit.</div>

